 grayscale opacity-40\">🐶</div></div><h3 class=\"jsx-80debf708dd09952 text-slate-900 font-bold text-lg mb-2 tracking-tight\">Waiting for location...</h3><p class=\"jsx-80debf708dd09952 text-slate-500 font-medium text-sm\">Enter your city on the left to see if it&#x27;s safe for a walk!</p></div></div></div></div><div class=\"jsx-80debf708dd09952 text-center mt-4 flex justify-center items-center gap-2\"><span class=\"jsx-80debf708dd09952 h-px w-10 bg-gradient-to-r from-transparent via-white/30 to-transparent\"></span><span class=\"jsx-80debf708dd09952 text-[10px] text-white/50 font-semibold uppercase tracking-wider px-3 py-1 rounded-full bg-white/5 backdrop-blur-sm border border-white/10\">Powered by Open-Meteo</span><span class=\"jsx-80debf708dd09952 h-px w-10 bg-gradient-to-r from-transparent via-white/30 to-transparent\"></span></div></div></div><footer class=\"footer-new\"><div class=\"footer-container\"><div class=\"footer-grid\"><div class=\"footer-column\"><h4 class=\"footer-heading\">IndoorDogPark</h4><ul class=\"footer-links\"><li><a href=\"/about\">About us</a></li><li><a href=\"/partners\">Partners</a></li></ul></div><div class=\"footer-column\"><h4 class=\"footer-heading\">Discover</h4><ul class=\"footer-links\"><li><a href=\"/\">Browse parks</a></li><li><a href=\"/how-it-works\">How it works</a></li><li><a href=\"/blog\">Blog</a></li></ul></div><div class=\"footer-column\"><h4 class=\"footer-heading\">Park Owners</h4><ul class=\"footer-links\"><li><a href=\"/list-your-park\">List your park</a></li><li><a href=\"/owner-resources\">Owner resources</a></li></ul></div><div class=\"footer-column\"><h4 class=\"footer-heading\">Support</h4><ul class=\"footer-links\"><li><a href=\"/contact\">Contact us</a></li><li><a href=\"/faq\">FAQ</a></li></ul></div><div class=\"footer-column col-span-full md:col-span-2 lg:col-span-1\"><h4 class=\"footer-heading\">Join the Pack</h4><p class=\"mb-4 text-sm text-white/70\">Get the latest indoor dog park news and updates.</p><d